  "detailed_description": "Ninja　dash! Ninja jump! Ninja slash!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n8-bit style Ninja platform action game!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn this fresh take on ninja-based action games, use your ninja to battle the monster army!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGet ready for some excitement in your life with this fast-paced action game, filled with the type of exhilarating energy that only ninjas possess!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFrom katanas, to throwing knives, to ninjutsu, you must master your ninja skills in order to save the kidnapped princess!",
